      </header>
      <p>If you are a developer working with web technologies, Crosswalk enables you to deploy a web application with its own dedicated runtime. This means three things:</p>
      <p>With Crosswalk, developers working with web technologies don’t have to worry about breaking whatever ancient <code>WebView</code> or browsers their audience is using.</p>
      <h3>Supported platforms</h3>
      <p>Your app will have the Crosswalk WebView in place of the unpredictable device default. Crosswalk is great for:</p>
